1953;;Marry Me Again;;American;;Frank Tashlin;;Robert Cummings, Marie Wilson;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marry_Me_Again;;Bill has an unusual dilemma when he returns home from the war in Korea, where he'd been a pilot. Out of pride, he wants to provide the sole support for Doris and their family, but Doris isn't sure what to do because she has just inherited a fortune.